Date: Thu, 21 May 2026 11:37:28 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 18/48] Surface plugin commands in the command palette + run
 with toast (oh-my-warp)

A PluginCommandDataSource reads the plugin command registry and yields synthetic
'plugin:<id>' CommandBindings (reusing existing rendering). The palette accept
handler recognizes the prefix, invokes the plugin callback via CallJsFunctionService,
and shows the returned string as an ephemeral toast. See PLUGIN_SPEC.md (M1).
